**BrightHelp is a Canadian virtual assistant matching platform with a built-in Workspace for small businesses, virtual assistants, and growing teams.**  
It helps clients find reliable support and gives VAs a calm, organized place to manage communication, tasks, files, and client operations.

Website: https://brighthelp.ca

