## ğŸŒ¼ How BrightHelp Works

### For Clients
1. Submit an intake form  
2. Receive a personalized shortlist of VAs  
3. Meet your matches  
4. Start working together inside your shared Workspace  
5. Keep communication, tasks, and files organized  

### For Virtual Assistants
1. Join BrightHelp as a member  
2. Set up your Workspace  
3. Bring your own clients or receive matches  
4. Track tasks, store files, and manage communication  
5. Create a smoother client experience  

